OL,3,CScotland's main political party
OL,4,Cleaders set for first TV debate of
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FThe leaders of Scotland's main
OL,8,Fpolitical parties will take part in
OL,9,Fthe first TV election debate of the
OL,10,Fcampaign on Sunday.
OL,12,FLeaders of the Scottish National
OL,13,FParty, Scottish Labour, Scottish
OL,14,FConservatives, Scottish Greens,
OL,15,FScottish Liberal Democrats and Reform
OL,16,FUK Scotland will take part in Debate
OL,17,FNight on the BBC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776059756
OL,3,CScotland's main political party
OL,4,Cleaders set for first TV debate of
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FThey will be asked questions by a live
OL,8,Fstudio audience, with issues such as
OL,9,Fthe cost-of-living, energy crisis and
OL,10,Fthe NHS likely to come up.
OL,12,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar has
OL,13,Fmade calls for SNP leader and First
OL,14,FMinister John Swinney to apologise at
OL,15,Fthe start of the televised debate for
OL,16,Fthe Scottish Government's handling of
OL,17,Fthe NHS.
OL,19,FMr Sarwar said: "Our NHS is not safe
OL,20,Fwith John Swinney and the SNP.
OL,26,@{D@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776059756
OL,3,CScotland's main political party
OL,4,Cleaders set for first TV debate of
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,F"They have now broken Scotland's NHS
OL,8,Ftreatment law 918,594 times, leaving
OL,9,Fpatients waiting in pain because they
OL,10,Ffailed to run the NHS properly.
OL,12,F"Tonight on television, right at start
OL,13,Fof the debate, John Swinney should
OL,14,Fapologise to every single patient who
OL,15,Fhas suffered because the SNP could not
OL,16,Fget the basics right.
OL,18,F"My first priority as First Minister
OL,19,Fwill be to cut waiting lists and put
OL,20,Four NHS first so it is there when you
OL,21,Fneed it.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776059756
OL,3,CScotland's main political party
OL,4,Cleaders set for first TV debate of
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,F"That means using all available
OL,8,Fcapacity to get patients treated
OL,9,Ffaster, breaking down barriers between
OL,10,Fhealth boards, and making sure funding
OL,11,Ffollows the patient so the NHS focuses
OL,12,Fon getting people care on time.
OL,14,F"After two decades of broken promises,
OL,15,Four NHS cannot survive another SNP
OL,16,Fgovernment.
OL,18,F"On May 7, vote Scottish Labour on
OL,19,Fboth votes for the change Scotland
OL,20,Fneeds."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
