OL,3,CScotland's main political party
OL,4,Cleaders set for first TV debate of
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FHowever, polls are showing that the
OL,8,FSNP are looking likely to stay in
OL,9,Foffice, with the first YouGov MRP
OL,10,Fsurvey of the election season
OL,11,Fsuggesting they are set to win 67
OL,12,Fseats.
OL,14,FThe poll projects that Reform UK are
OL,15,Fon course to win 20 MSPs with Labour
OL,16,Festimated to win no constituency seats
OL,17,Fat all, picking up just 15 seats from
OL,18,Fthe regional lists.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
