PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776059756
OL,3,CScotland's main political party
OL,4,Cleaders set for first TV debate of
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FThe Greens are projected to win 11
OL,8,Fseats and the Lib Dems are set to win
OL,9,Fnine, showing gains between them.
OL,11,FThe poll suggests the Conservatives
OL,12,Fcould be looking at a sixth place
OL,13,Ffinish and are projected to win just
OL,14,Fseven seats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
