OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776059756
OL,3,CScotland's main political party
OL,4,Cleaders set for first TV debate of
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FSNP candidate for Rutherglen Clare
OL,8,FHaughey responded to Mr Sarwar's
OL,9,Fcomments, saying: "Of course there are
OL,10,Fchallenges, just as there are across
OL,11,Fthese islands, but the fact is John
OL,12,FSwinney has a plan for our NHS and
OL,13,Fit's working.
OL,15,F"While Anas Sarwar talks our NHS down,
OL,16,Funder our plan operations are up,
OL,17,Fwaiting lists continue to fall, we
OL,18,Fhave more GPs per head than England
OL,19,Fand our GP walk-in centres are
OL,20,Fspringing up across Scotland.
OL,26,@qD@SOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
