PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776059756
OL,3,CScotland's main political party
OL,4,Cleaders set for first TV debate of
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,F"Labour-run England is paying doctors
OL,8,F#20 per person to divert people away
OL,9,Ffrom their NHS and faces yet another
OL,10,FNHS strike ` not a single day has been
OL,11,Flost to strikes in Scotland's NHS
OL,12,Fthanks to the SNP in government.
OL,14,F"Only the SNP can be trusted with
OL,15,FScotland's NHS ` that's exactly what
OL,16,Fyou get from John Swinney's strong
OL,17,Fleadership and that's what's on the
OL,18,Fballot on 7th May."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
