OL,3,CScotland's main political party
OL,4,Cleaders set for first TV debate of
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FThe debate will be moderated by
OL,8,FStephen Jardine who wrote in the
OL,9,FScotsman on Saturday that the debate
OL,10,Fmay be dictated around which lines
OL,11,Fwill end up being popular on social
OL,12,Fmedia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
