OL,3,CScotland's main political party
OL,4,Cleaders set for first TV debate of
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FHe said: "Often they have spent days
OL,8,Fpreparing, trying out attack lines,
OL,9,Ftesting defensive positions and
OL,10,Fthinking about how they can cut
OL,11,Fthrough and make an impression.
OL,12,FNowadays another factor is also in
OL,13,Fplay. Increasingly, political debates
OL,14,Fare less about the whole show and more
OL,15,Fabout what ends up being a short clip
OL,16,Fon social media."
OL,26,@oD@JOUxD@QO]
